{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01QhaJR7Ldovg9FEjzo54HYE","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package com.example.orderspring.service;\n     2→\n     3→import jakarta.annotation.PostConstruct;\n     4→import jakarta.ejb.EJB;\n     5→import jakarta.ejb.Singleton;\n     6→import jakarta.ejb.Startup;\n     7→import jakarta.ejb.TransactionManagement;\n     8→import jakarta.ejb.TransactionManagementType;\n     9→import jakarta.annotation.Resource;\n    10→import jakarta.transaction.UserTransaction;\n    11→import java.util.logging.Level;\n    12→import java.util.logging.Logger;\n    13→\n    14→@Singleton\n    15→@Startup\n    16→@TransactionManagement(TransactionManagementType.BEAN)\n    17→public class DataInitializationService {\n    18→\n    19→    private static final Logger logger = Logger.getLogger(\"order.service.DataInitializationService\");\n    20→\n    21→    @EJB\n    22→    private OrderService orderService;\n    23→\n    24→    @Resource\n    25→    private UserTransaction utx;\n    26→\n    27→    @PostConstruct\n    28→    public void onApplicationReady() {\n    29→        try {\n    30→            utx.begin();\n    31→            createInitialData();\n    32→            utx.commit();\n    33→        } catch (Exception e) {\n    34→            logger.log(Level.SEVERE, \"Error initializing data\", e);\n    35→            try {\n    36→                utx.rollback();\n    37→            } catch (Exception ex) {\n    38→                logger.log(Level.SEVERE, \"Error rolling back\", ex);\n    39→            }\n    40→        }\n    41→    }\n    42→\n    43→    private void createInitialData() {\n    44→        // Create parts\n    45→        orderService.createPart(\"1234-5678-01\", 1, \"ABC PART\",\n    46→                new java.util.Date(), \"PARTQWERTYUIOPASXDCFVGBHNJMKL\", null);\n    47→        orderService.createPart(\"9876-4321-02\", 2, \"DEF PART\",\n    48→                new java.util.Date(), \"PARTQWERTYUIOPASXDCFVGBHNJMKL\", null);\n    49→        orderService.createPart(\"5456-6789-03\", 3, \"GHI PART\",\n    50→                new java.util.Date(), \"PARTQWERTYUIOPASXDCFVGBHNJMKL\", null);\n    51→        orderService.createPart(\"ABCD-XYZW-FF\", 5, \"XYZ PART\",\n    52→                new java.util.Date(), \"PARTQWERTYUIOPASXDCFVGBHNJMKL\", null);\n    53→        orderService.createPart(\"SDFG-ERTY-BN\", 7, \"BOM PART\",\n    54→                new java.util.Date(), \"PARTQWERTYUIOPASXDCFVGBHNJMKL\", null);\n    55→\n    56→        // Add parts to bill of materials\n    57→        orderService.addPartToBillOfMaterial(\"SDFG-ERTY-BN\", 7, \"1234-5678-01\", 1);\n    58→        orderService.addPartToBillOfMaterial(\"SDFG-ERTY-BN\", 7, \"9876-4321-02\", 2);\n    59→        orderService.addPartToBillOfMaterial(\"SDFG-ERTY-BN\", 7, \"5456-6789-03\", 3);\n    60→        orderService.addPartToBillOfMaterial(\"SDFG-ERTY-BN\", 7, \"ABCD-XYZW-FF\", 5);\n    61→\n    62→        // Create vendors\n    63→        orderService.createVendor(100, \"WidgetCorp\",\n    64→                \"111 Main St., Anytown, KY 99999\", \"Mr. Jones\",\n    65→                \"888-777-9999\");\n    66→        orderService.createVendor(200, \"Gadget, Inc.\",\n    67→                \"123 State St., Sometown, MI 88888\", \"Mrs. Smith\",\n    68→                \"866-345-6789\");\n    69→\n    70→        // Create vendor parts\n    71→        orderService.createVendorPart(\"1234-5678-01\", 1, \"PART1\", 100.00, 100);\n    72→        orderService.createVendorPart(\"9876-4321-02\", 2, \"PART2\", 10.44, 200);\n    73→        orderService.createVendorPart(\"5456-6789-03\", 3, \"PART3\", 76.23, 200);\n    74→        orderService.createVendorPart(\"ABCD-XYZW-FF\", 5, \"PART4\", 55.19, 100);\n    75→        orderService.createVendorPart(\"SDFG-ERTY-BN\", 7, \"PART5\", 345.87, 100);\n    76→\n    77→        // Create orders\n    78→        Integer orderId = 1111;\n    79→        orderService.createOrder(orderId, 'N', 10, \"333 New Court, New City, CA 90000\");\n    80→        orderService.addLineItem(orderId, \"1234-5678-01\", 1, 3);\n    81→        orderService.addLineItem(orderId, \"9876-4321-02\", 2, 5);\n    82→        orderService.addLineItem(orderId, \"ABCD-XYZW-FF\", 5, 7);\n    83→\n    84→        orderId = 4312;\n    85→        orderService.createOrder(orderId, 'N', 0, \"333 New Court, New City, CA 90000\");\n    86→        orderService.addLineItem(orderId, \"SDFG-ERTY-BN\", 7, 1);\n    87→        orderService.addLineItem(orderId, \"ABCD-XYZW-FF\", 5, 3);\n    88→        orderService.addLineItem(orderId, \"1234-5678-01\", 1, 15);\n    89→    }\n    90→}\n    91→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c75ef7e1-cdcb-4fc9-ba4d-53d982e17ac3","uuid":"e4a3fbe0-ba01-4b21-a935-f2e6389351dc"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01GJJSafxrzQVSxk4NJdT6Gx","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package com.example.orderspring;\n     2→\n     3→import jakarta.ws.rs.ApplicationPath;\n     4→import jakarta.ws.rs.core.Application;\n     5→\n     6→@ApplicationPath(\"/api\")\n     7→public class OrderApplication extends Application {\n     8→}\n     9→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c75ef7e1-cdcb-4fc9-ba4d-53d982e17ac3","uuid":"1207f3da-77a7-403c-9823-d350af2b7907"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01YRb4knBSUYhCLf8wTpXZtC","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package com.example.orderspring.web;\n     2→\n     3→import com.example.orderspring.entity.CustomerOrder;\n     4→import com.example.orderspring.entity.LineItem;\n     5→import com.example.orderspring.entity.Part;\n     6→import com.example.orderspring.entity.Vendor;\n     7→import com.example.orderspring.service.OrderService;\n     8→import jakarta.ejb.EJB;\n     9→import jakarta.ws.rs.*;\n    10→import jakarta.ws.rs.core.MediaType;\n    11→import jakarta.ws.rs.core.Response;\n    12→import jakarta.json.Json;\n    13→import jakarta.json.JsonArrayBuilder;\n    14→import jakarta.json.JsonObjectBuilder;\n    15→\n    16→import java.util.List;\n    17→\n    18→@Path(\"/orders\")\n    19→@Produces(MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON)\n    20→public class OrderResource {\n    21→\n    22→    @EJB\n    23→    private OrderService orderService;\n    24→\n    25→    @GET\n    26→    public Response getAllOrders() {\n    27→        List<CustomerOrder> orders = orderService.getAllOrders();\n    28→        JsonArrayBuilder array = Json.createArrayBuilder();\n    29→        for (CustomerOrder order : orders) {\n    30→            JsonObjectBuilder obj = Json.createObjectBuilder()\n    31→                .add(\"orderId\", order.getOrderId())\n    32→                .add(\"status\", String.valueOf(order.getStatus()))\n    33→                .add(\"discount\", order.getDiscount())\n    34→                .add(\"shipmentInfo\", order.getShipmentInfo() != null ? order.getShipmentInfo() : \"\");\n    35→            array.add(obj);\n    36→        }\n    37→        return Response.ok(array.build().toString()).build();\n    38→    }\n    39→\n    40→    @GET\n    41→    @Path(\"/{orderId}\")\n    42→    public Response getOrder(@PathParam(\"orderId\") Integer orderId) {\n    43→        var orderOpt = orderService.getOrders().stream()\n    44→                .filter(o -> o.getOrderId().equals(orderId))\n    45→                .findFirst();\n    46→        if (orderOpt.isEmpty()) {\n    47→            return Response.status(Response.Status.NOT_FOUND).build();\n    48→        }\n    49→        CustomerOrder order = orderOpt.get();\n    50→        JsonObjectBuilder obj = Json.createObjectBuilder()\n    51→            .add(\"orderId\", order.getOrderId())\n    52→            .add(\"status\", String.valueOf(order.getStatus()))\n    53→            .add(\"discount\", order.getDiscount())\n    54→            .add(\"shipmentInfo\", order.getShipmentInfo() != null ? order.getShipmentInfo() : \"\");\n    55→        return Response.ok(obj.build().toString()).build();\n    56→    }\n    57→\n    58→    @GET\n    59→    @Path(\"/{orderId}/lineitems\")\n    60→    public Response getLineItems(@PathParam(\"orderId\") Integer orderId) {\n    61→        List<LineItem> items = orderService.getLineItemsByOrderId(orderId);\n    62→        JsonArrayBuilder array = Json.createArrayBuilder();\n    63→        for (LineItem item : items) {\n    64→            JsonObjectBuilder obj = Json.createObjectBuilder()\n    65→                .add(\"itemId\", item.getItemId())\n    66→                .add(\"quantity\", item.getQuantity());\n    67→            if (item.getVendorPart() != null) {\n    68→                obj.add(\"vendorPartNumber\", item.getVendorPart().getVendorPartNumber());\n    69→            }\n    70→            array.add(obj);\n    71→        }\n    72→        return Response.ok(array.build().toString()).build();\n    73→    }\n    74→\n    75→    @GET\n    76→    @Path(\"/parts\")\n    77→    public Response getAllParts() {\n    78→        List<Part> parts = orderService.getAllParts();\n    79→        JsonArrayBuilder array = Json.createArrayBuilder();\n    80→        for (Part part : parts) {\n    81→            JsonObjectBuilder obj = Json.createObjectBuilder()\n    82→                .add(\"partNumber\", part.getPartNumber())\n    83→                .add(\"revision\", part.getRevision())\n    84→                .add(\"description\", part.getDescription() != null ? part.getDescription() : \"\");\n    85→            array.add(obj);\n    86→        }\n    87→        return Response.ok(array.build().toString()).build();\n    88→    }\n    89→\n    90→    @GET\n    91→    @Path(\"/vendors/search\")\n    92→    public Response searchVendors(@QueryParam(\"name\") String name) {\n    93→        List<Vendor> vendors = orderService.findVendorsByName(name);\n    94→        JsonArrayBuilder array = Json.createArrayBuilder();\n    95→        for (Vendor vendor : vendors) {\n    96→            JsonObjectBuilder obj = Json.createObjectBuilder()\n    97→                .add(\"vendorId\", vendor.getVendorId())\n    98→                .add(\"name\", vendor.getName() != null ? vendor.getName() : \"\")\n    99→                .add(\"contact\", vendor.getContact() != null ? vendor.getContact() : \"\");\n   100→            array.add(obj);\n   101→        }\n   102→        return Response.ok(array.build().toString()).build();\n   103→    }\n   104→\n   105→    @GET\n   106→    @Path(\"/health\")\n   107→    public Response health() {\n   108→        return Response.ok(\"{\\\"status\\\":\\\"UP\\\"}\").build();\n   109→    }\n   110→}\n   111→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c75ef7e1-cdcb-4fc9-ba4d-53d982e17ac3","uuid":"afcab471-24a1-4cac-a520-0f56156d42ab"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Bd3vd57qP8L9VSBZmFBUEQ","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package com.example.orderspring.web;\n     2→\n     3→import com.example.orderspring.entity.CustomerOrder;\n     4→import com.example.orderspring.entity.LineItem;\n     5→import com.example.orderspring.entity.Part;\n     6→import com.example.orderspring.entity.Vendor;\n     7→import com.example.orderspring.service.OrderService;\n     8→import jakarta.ejb.EJB;\n     9→import jakarta.enterprise.context.SessionScoped;\n    10→import jakarta.inject.Named;\n    11→import jakarta.faces.context.FacesContext;\n    12→import jakarta.faces.event.ActionEvent;\n    13→import java.io.Serializable;\n    14→import java.util.List;\n    15→\n    16→@Named(\"orderManager\")\n    17→@SessionScoped\n    18→public class OrderManager implements Serializable {\n    19→    private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;\n    20→\n    21→    @EJB\n    22→    private OrderService orderService;\n    23→\n    24→    private List<CustomerOrder> orders;\n    25→    private List<LineItem> lineItems;\n    26→    private List<Part> parts;\n    27→    private List<Vendor> vendorSearchResults;\n    28→\n    29→    private Integer currentOrder;\n    30→    private Integer newOrderId;\n    31→    private String newOrderShippingInfo;\n    32→    private Character newOrderStatus = 'P';\n    33→    private Integer newOrderDiscount = 0;\n    34→    private String vendorName;\n    35→    private boolean findVendorTableDisabled = true;\n    36→\n    37→    private List<Part> newOrderParts;\n    38→    private String selectedPartNumber;\n    39→    private Integer selectedPartRevision;\n    40→    private Long selectedVendorPartNumber;\n    41→\n    42→    public List<CustomerOrder> getOrders() {\n    43→        if (orders == null) {\n    44→            orders = orderService.getAllOrders();\n    45→        }\n    46→        return orders;\n    47→    }\n    48→    public void setOrders(List<CustomerOrder> orders) { this.orders = orders; }\n    49→\n    50→    public List<LineItem> getLineItems() {\n    51→        if (lineItems == null && currentOrder != null) {\n    52→            lineItems = orderService.getLineItemsByOrderId(currentOrder);\n    53→        }\n    54→        return lineItems;\n    55→    }\n    56→    public void setLineItems(List<LineItem> lineItems) { this.lineItems = lineItems; }\n    57→\n    58→    public List<Part> getParts() {\n    59→        if (parts == null) {\n    60→            parts = orderService.getAllParts();\n    61→        }\n    62→        return parts;\n    63→    }\n    64→    public void setParts(List<Part> parts) { this.parts = parts; }\n    65→\n    66→    public List<Vendor> getVendorSearchResults() { return vendorSearchResults; }\n    67→    public void setVendorSearchResults(List<Vendor> vendorSearchResults) { this.vendorSearchResults = vendorSearchResults; }\n    68→\n    69→    public Integer getCurrentOrder() { return currentOrder; }\n    70→    public void setCurrentOrder(Integer currentOrder) {\n    71→        this.currentOrder = currentOrder;\n    72→        this.lineItems = null;\n    73→    }\n    74→\n    75→    public Integer getNewOrderId() { return newOrderId; }\n    76→    public void setNewOrderId(Integer newOrderId) { this.newOrderId = newOrderId; }\n    77→\n    78→    public String getNewOrderShippingInfo() { return newOrderShippingInfo; }\n    79→    public void setNewOrderShippingInfo(String newOrderShippingInfo) { this.newOrderShippingInfo = newOrderShippingInfo; }\n    80→\n    81→    public Character getNewOrderStatus() { return newOrderStatus; }\n    82→    public void setNewOrderStatus(Character newOrderStatus) { this.newOrderStatus = newOrderStatus; }\n    83→\n    84→    public Integer getNewOrderDiscount() { return newOrderDiscount; }\n    85→    public void setNewOrderDiscount(Integer newOrderDiscount) { this.newOrderDiscount = newOrderDiscount; }\n    86→\n    87→    public String getVendorName() { return vendorName; }\n    88→    public void setVendorName(String vendorName) { this.vendorName = vendorName; }\n    89→\n    90→    public boolean isFindVendorTableDisabled() { return findVendorTableDisabled; }\n    91→    public void setFindVendorTableDisabled(boolean findVendorTableDisabled) { this.findVendorTableDisabled = findVendorTableDisabled; }\n    92→\n    93→    public List<Part> getNewOrderParts() {\n    94→        if (newOrderParts == null) {\n    95→            newOrderParts = orderService.getAllParts();\n    96→        }\n    97→        return newOrderParts;\n    98→    }\n    99→    public void setNewOrderParts(List<Part> newOrderParts) { this.newOrderParts = newOrderParts; }\n   100→\n   101→    public String getSelectedPartNumber() { return selectedPartNumber; }\n   102→    public void setSelectedPartNumber(String selectedPartNumber) { this.selectedPartNumber = selectedPartNumber; }\n   103→\n   104→    public Integer getSelectedPartRevision() { return selectedPartRevision; }\n   105→    public void setSelectedPartRevision(Integer selectedPartRevision) { this.selectedPartRevision = selectedPartRevision; }\n   106→\n   107→    public Long getSelectedVendorPartNumber() { return selectedVendorPartNumber; }\n   108→    public void setSelectedVendorPartNumber(Long selectedVendorPartNumber) { this.selectedVendorPartNumber = selectedVendorPartNumber; }\n   109→\n   110→    public String submitOrder() {\n   111→        try {\n   112→            if (newOrderId == null) return \"order\";\n   113→            char status = (newOrderStatus != null ? newOrderStatus : 'P');\n   114→            int discount = (newOrderDiscount != null ? newOrderDiscount : 0);\n   115→            orderService.createOrder(newOrderId, status, discount, newOrderShippingInfo);\n   116→            newOrderId = null;\n   117→            newOrderShippingInfo = null;\n   118→            newOrderStatus = 'P';\n   119→            newOrderDiscount = 0;\n   120→            orders = null;\n   121→            if (currentOrder != null) lineItems = null;\n   122→            return \"order\";\n   123→        } catch (Exception e) {\n   124→            e.printStackTrace();\n   125→            return \"order\";\n   126→        }\n   127→    }\n   128→\n   129→    public String removeOrder() {\n   130→        try {\n   131→            if (currentOrder != null) {\n   132→                orderService.removeOrder(currentOrder);\n   133→                orders = null;\n   134→                lineItems = null;\n   135→                currentOrder = null;\n   136→            }\n   137→            return \"order\";\n   138→        } catch (Exception e) {\n   139→            e.printStackTrace();\n   140→            return \"order\";\n   141→        }\n   142→    }\n   143→\n   144→    public void removeOrder(ActionEvent event) {\n   145→        String id = FacesContext.getCurrentInstance()\n   146→                .getExternalContext()\n   147→                .getRequestParameterMap()\n   148→                .get(\"deleteOrderId\");\n   149→        if (id != null && !id.isBlank()) {\n   150→            Integer orderId = Integer.valueOf(id);\n   151→            orderService.removeOrder(orderId);\n   152→            orders = null;\n   153→            lineItems = null;\n   154→            if (orderId.equals(currentOrder)) currentOrder = null;\n   155→        }\n   156→    }\n   157→\n   158→    public String findVendor() {\n   159→        try {\n   160→            vendorSearchResults = orderService.findVendorsByName(vendorName);\n   161→            findVendorTableDisabled = false;\n   162→            return \"order\";\n   163→        } catch (Exception e) {\n   164→            e.printStackTrace();\n   165→            findVendorTableDisabled = true;\n   166→            return \"order\";\n   167→        }\n   168→    }\n   169→\n   170→    public String addLineItem() {\n   171→        try {\n   172→            if (currentOrder != null && selectedPartNumber != null && selectedPartRevision != null) {\n   173→                orderService.addLineItem(currentOrder, selectedPartNumber, selectedPartRevision, 1);\n   174→                lineItems = null;\n   175→            }\n   176→            return \"lineItem\";\n   177→        } catch (Exception e) {\n   178→            e.printStackTrace();\n   179→            return \"lineItem\";\n   180→        }\n   181→    }\n   182→\n   183→    public String lineItem() { return \"lineItem\"; }\n   184→    public String order() { return \"order\"; }\n   185→}\n   186→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c75ef7e1-cdcb-4fc9-ba4d-53d982e17ac3","uuid":"2982d5e5-0baa-477a-b006-73db808324f0"}
