{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_014dpVGNymtfDGDD6WCzsxKc","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The migration is complete. Here's a summary of what was accomplished:\n\n## Migration Complete: Spring Boot 3.3.7 -> Jakarta EE 10 (Open Liberty)\n\n### Key Changes\n- **Runtime**: Spring Boot embedded Tomcat -> Open Liberty (Jakarta EE 10)\n- **Packaging**: executable JAR -> WAR deployed to Liberty\n- **Repositories**: 5 Spring Data JPA interfaces -> `@Stateless` EJB classes with `EntityManager` + JPQL\n- **Services**: `@Service`/`@Component` -> `@Stateless`/`@Singleton` EJBs\n- **DI**: `@Autowired` -> `@EJB`\n- **Startup**: `@EventListener(ApplicationReadyEvent)` -> `@Singleton @Startup @PostConstruct` with BMT\n- **Configuration**: `application.properties` -> `server.xml`, `persistence.xml`, `beans.xml`, `web.xml`\n- **New**: JAX-RS REST resource (`OrderResource.java`) for API access and smoke testing\n- **New**: `smoke.py` with 8 automated tests\n\n### Errors Resolved\n1. UBI package manager (`yum` not `apt-get`)\n2. EntityManager null in CDI beans (switched to `@Stateless` EJBs)\n3. Singleton `@PostConstruct` transaction rollback (switched to BMT with `UserTransaction`)\n4. H2 datasource URL format (generic properties element)\n5. ORB user registry requirement (added `<basicRegistry>`)\n6. EJB injection (`@EJB` instead of `@Inject`)\n\n### Test Results\n**8/8 smoke tests passed** - health, orders, order detail, line items, parts, vendor search, 404 handling, JSF page."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":661,"cache_read_input_tokens":74982,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":661,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":431},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c75ef7e1-cdcb-4fc9-ba4d-53d982e17ac3","uuid":"a61f1e0f-6e5a-46d6-9e05-59725201471f"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":2459077,"duration_api_ms":1961525,"num_turns":201,"result":"The migration is complete. Here's a summary of what was accomplished:\n\n## Migration Complete: Spring Boot 3.3.7 -> Jakarta EE 10 (Open Liberty)\n\n### Key Changes\n- **Runtime**: Spring Boot embedded Tomcat -> Open Liberty (Jakarta EE 10)\n- **Packaging**: executable JAR -> WAR deployed to Liberty\n- **Repositories**: 5 Spring Data JPA interfaces -> `@Stateless` EJB classes with `EntityManager` + JPQL\n- **Services**: `@Service`/`@Component` -> `@Stateless`/`@Singleton` EJBs\n- **DI**: `@Autowired` -> `@EJB`\n- **Startup**: `@EventListener(ApplicationReadyEvent)` -> `@Singleton @Startup @PostConstruct` with BMT\n- **Configuration**: `application.properties` -> `server.xml`, `persistence.xml`, `beans.xml`, `web.xml`\n- **New**: JAX-RS REST resource (`OrderResource.java`) for API access and smoke testing\n- **New**: `smoke.py` with 8 automated tests\n\n### Errors Resolved\n1. UBI package manager (`yum` not `apt-get`)\n2. EntityManager null in CDI beans (switched to `@Stateless` EJBs)\n3. Singleton `@PostConstruct` transaction rollback (switched to BMT with `UserTransaction`)\n4. H2 datasource URL format (generic properties element)\n5. ORB user registry requirement (added `<basicRegistry>`)\n6. EJB injection (`@EJB` instead of `@Inject`)\n\n### Test Results\n**8/8 smoke tests passed** - health, orders, order detail, line items, parts, vendor search, 404 handling, JSF page.","session_id":"c75ef7e1-cdcb-4fc9-ba4d-53d982e17ac3","total_cost_usd":29.471882820000026,"usage":{"input_tokens":166,"cache_creation_input_tokens":336341,"cache_read_input_tokens":10199177,"output_tokens":58762,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":336341}},"modelUsage":{"aws/claude-3-5-haiku":{"inputTokens":416641,"outputTokens":8831,"cacheRe